{
 "name": "RPlog_SW1_Log_2000-01-15",
 "title": "Unmasking Zenani Abotu",
 "summary": "Aboard a New Republic vessel's mess hall, the diplomat Poguala briefs Luke Skywalker on her hunt for infiltrating Sith agents while the medic Jasmine and the pilot Bazil McKenzie look on. Bazil delivers a datapad from Coruscant whose records confirm Poguala's suspicion that \"Zenani Abotu,\" a woman posing with false Tanaab parentage, is in fact the fallen former diplomat Morganna Tazecks. Jasmine's account of Zenani's mind-reading and cruelty toward Altair Quila corroborates the identification. Poguala lays plans to lure and detain the woman through legal warrants and a baited distraction, enlisting Bazil to contact Altair, while Luke secures a promise to be present for any questioning so he might judge whether the woman can be redeemed. The newcomer Wes Carter drifts in for a quiet drink as the group disperses for the night.",
